    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">武器@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_DMTools.homebrewrolltable.RollTable.D3VgPrWARtKdRRF8]{（任意劍）}</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;FLOAT:none;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">這柄劍的黑色劍刃由一種神秘的奧術合金所製成。你在用該魔法武器發動攻擊檢定與傷害擲骰時獲得</span>+1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">加值。攜帶此劍時，你免疫將你轉化為不死的效應。</span></p><ul><li><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;FLOAT:none;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">黑暗饋贈</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;FLOAT:none;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">持握此劍時，你可以用一個動作使自己獲得[[/r 1d4+4 #冥河之劍 - 黑暗饋贈]]</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">點臨時生命值。第二天黃昏前，此特性無法再次使用。</span></p></li><li><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;FLOAT:none;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">沮喪打擊</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;FLOAT:none;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">你使用此武器發動攻擊並命中一個生物時，你可以讓該目標的內心充滿恐懼與不安。在你的下一回合結束前，該目標進行的的下一次豁免具有劣勢。免疫恐慌的生物將不受此特性影響。第二天黃昏前，此特性無法再次使用。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></p></li></ul></div>",
